Output demo-terminal.gif

Set FontSize 24
Set Width 1280
Set Height 720
Set Padding 40
Set Theme "Light"

Type "Use $exhibit-interaction-diagram to 把这个展项创意生成一张清晰能看懂玩法的装置交互图"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type "1. prompt-brief: 判断玩法、空间、硬件、人物和反馈内容"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "2. runtime-prompt: 只保留当前命题相关规则，生成一张图"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Type "3. qa-checklist: 检查人是否参与、设备距离、可达范围和主题信息"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "Result: a readable exhibit interaction diagram, not a poster or hardware inventory."
Sleep 1200ms

